1. ZKsync founder responds to security incident: no code or key leaks, full investigation results will be released;
2. GMGN launches Meme real-time tweet preview and real-time pool monitoring functions;
3.5 suspected related wallets spent $4.28 million to buy more than 611 billion PEPE, funds from Tornado Cash;
4. MELANIA project sold 20.5 million tokens in one month, cashing out about $14.06 million;
5. After Unichain launched a $5 million incentive plan, 24H cross-chain inflow exceeded $22 million;
6. Multiple institutions transferred more than 24,000 ETH to exchanges within 24 hours;
7. Trump said that US tariff revenue hit a record high, and prices and inflation fell simultaneously;
8. Analysis shows that BTC bullish sentiment has warmed up, and Binance's buying and selling ratio has returned to the neutral zone
9. TRUMP project party withdrew 460 by removing liquidity 13 hours ago 10. Ethereum spot ETF had a total net outflow of 14.1821 million US dollars yesterday, and continued to have net outflows for 6 days; 11. The crypto market generally fell, BTC fell below 84,000 US dollars, and ETH fell below 1,600 US dollars.
